{"tid":2495761,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"凝冰解凍 花必定重開","createTime":"2021-04-19T11:17:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T11:28:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"210b4d39db8a8187be6e19f608953ca6fb36ab2a","tid":2495761,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T11:17:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210419/SLVETUZJJFDYTNB3JUMASADBDU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210419%2FSLVETUZJJFDYTNB3JUMASADBDU%2F&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqxw2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=0b693ccc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210419%2FSLVETUZJJFDYTNB3JUMASADBDU%2F&h=0a95c8e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210419/SLVETUZJJFDYTNB3JUMASADBDU/</a><br />\n<br />\n凝冰解凍 花必定重開<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/9ESmpImlXmV2fdO7dfpHVz6npZU=/802x577/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/N7YG4IOMUBABBLZO5ZVZLZN5XE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F9ESmpImlXmV2fdO7dfpHVz6npZU%3D%2F802x577%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FN7YG4IOMUBABBLZO5ZVZLZN5XE.jpg&h=3dc65130&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n極權不單早視民主與人權如無物，近日更肆無忌憚抹黑攻擊傳媒，新聞自由早已敲響喪鐘，透過報章為平台向失去自由的手足送上鼓勵和支持，不再是必然，但如港人的誓約：只要一息尚存，《蘋果》必繼續向牆內送暖。<br />\n<br />\n有讀者來鴻給朱凱廸，鼓勵他不要忘記有認識和不認識的朋友都為他打氣；有首當寫信師的讀者致函楊岳橋，感激對方為港人請命，約定彼此在自由法治公義的香港煲底相見；「初心」向之鋒寄語，黑暗盡頭會見光明。願微小的送暖祝福，成為手足們苦中一點甜。<br />\n<br />\n讀者電郵請發送到letterstoprison@appledaily.com，或來函將軍澳工業邨駿盈街8號 《蘋果日報》編輯部<br />\n<br />\n送暖高牆逢周一至五刊出<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【盼同呼吸自由空氣】<br />\n<br />\n我睇到《蘋果日報》，有寫信師邀請，本人一直欣賞楊律師你詞鋒尖銳，亦有感楊律師為人光明磊落，為香港人請命，深受感動，決定開始我寫信師生涯，而第一封信，我希望係寫畀你 ！<br />\n<br />\n作為一個土生土長嘅香港人，睇住香港變化，睇住香港淪落到如斯境況，又怎會不流淚 ！<br />\n<br />\n相信，你同我哋都一樣，同樣感到痛心！<br />\n<br />\n我哋其實真係好多謝一班民主派，我自己特別想多謝你，多謝你同民主派，一直不畏極權，為我哋香港人發聲，多謝晒！<br />\n<br />\n知道你哋被政府玩弄法例，被未審先囚，被無理非法禁錮，但我哋香港人能幫你哋做的，確實沒有，對唔住，希望你可以原諒我哋呢班幫唔到手嘅香港人。<br />\n<br />\n我只想用文字，講我心入面感受，同你及每一位被極權無理非法殘害嘅民主派人士講，香港人好多謝你哋，我哋好愛你哋每一位，你哋要好好保護自己生命身體，希望好快，你同香港人，可以喺自由法治公義嘅香港煲底，可以呼吸住自由法治公義嘅空氣相見 ！<br />\n<br />\n土生土長香港人<br />\n<br />\n杜麗華<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【蘇軾被貶 不忘詩詞】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/RpqCKnXWP3t-HgkxRkyn0qN3eXk=/802x984/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SUMI7C5SA5F5FNLG7SUF2L3FHM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRpqCKnXWP3t-HgkxRkyn0qN3eXk%3D%2F802x984%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSUMI7C5SA5F5FNLG7SUF2L3FHM.jpg&h=03389065&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n先生你好︰<br />\n<br />\n看見你的名字，我會想到一位好瘦戴眼鏡的文弱書生。在我腦海中浮現你踏單車跑遍很多鄉村的影像。我的一位舊生還幫你貼海報呢！<br />\n<br />\n那天我由朗屏站一路走，希望找到去天水圍的山路。一路上，兩邊有很多山墳，大大小小，好像走進一個墳場。遠望元朗市區景物，一點都不吸引。但令我感覺怪怪的是有些墳地很大，有的還建造了牌坊！有貧富懸殊的感覺呢！<br />\n<br />\n天氣漸熱，希望你能忍受悶熱和可能有昆蟲作伴的環境！蘇東坡被貶官數次，他不忘作詩詞，心境最重要。<br />\n<br />\n別忘記有你認識和不認識的朋友為你打氣！加油啊！<br />\n<br />\nCK<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【願再看見燦爛微笑】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/IIqb5iAfiV2tFCRQAHDSaNqFHks=/802x1134/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PB33H26IAVA2FG75CLAR4OHNYQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FIIqb5iAfiV2tFCRQAHDSaNqFHks%3D%2F802x1134%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPB33H26IAVA2FG75CLAR4OHNYQ.jpg&h=0926d496&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【阿信精神走荊棘前路】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/rOjus8w-UZf72Z86n2PL7Y3PvXE=/802x849/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QRCER2BLYFCC5PWKMRS3ZNG32Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FrOjus8w-UZf72Z86n2PL7Y3PvXE%3D%2F802x849%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQRCER2BLYFCC5PWKMRS3ZNG32Q.jpg&h=510d6a5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/iwLlVRG1y7ESdCi2O3JzUXRy5os=/802x1134/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4LTMASLPORB5BIYXELRQCUYZHM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FiwLlVRG1y7ESdCi2O3JzUXRy5os%3D%2F802x1134%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4LTMASLPORB5BIYXELRQCUYZHM.jpg&h=3d4e8e32&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"819db864f755b047fa8b5a12d6119e4bf73e548f","tid":2495761,"uid":159271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T11:28:36.000Z","msg":"push"}]}